These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, airplane, bus, train
There 5 different types of food: carrot, kale, banana, cauliflower, asparagus
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person eating banana is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person eating carrot##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person driving the train is between the chinese and the person eating asparagus##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating kale##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Transport      | trike        | helicopter | train     | airplane   | bus |
| Food   | banana     | kale      | cauliflower | asparagus   | carrot    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

