.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, golf, basketball, badminton, rowing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, swisher, montecristo, blend, alhambra
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the chinese and the alhambra-smoker##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the indian is the blend-smoker##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the indian is the person who's sport is basketball##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Sport         | badminton | cricket | rowing    | golf  | basketball    |
| Cigar   | alhambra    | swisher       | montecristo      | game | blend        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

