.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, milk, fanta, almond-milk
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, lavender, orange, coral, yellow
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes pink is in the middle##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes coral##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage         | 7up | almond-milk     | milk   | water   | fanta |
| Color   | yellow  | lavender | pink | coral | orange        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

