.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, pink, green, lilac, fuchsia
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, skateboard, taxi, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is between the fan of reggae and the person who likes lilac##2
 5. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Color          | fuchsia  | green     | lilac   | pink     | apricot |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking    | singing  | skydiving | puzzles   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Transport   | bike    | skateboard | taxi | jet-ski | snowmobile   |

