 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
13. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
