 3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person eating lemon is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes turquise##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

