5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, poker, scrabble, monopoly
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, ship, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person playing poker is between the person eating watermelon and the egyptian##2
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person eating peach is in the middle##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is the turkish##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the person playing backgammon is the person eating nectarine##1
13. the person playing poker is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Food         | nectarine   | cabbage | peach  | kiwi | watermelon |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish     | egyptian   | french     | mexican      |
