The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, traveling, singing, magic-tricks
 1. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the accountant##1
 5. the journalist is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the videographer is the person eating spinach##1
 8. the person drinking tea is between the person eating blueberry and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the person eating watermelon is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |     3      |       4       |     5     |
