 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the canadian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking juice##2
11. the malaysian is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the polish is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
