.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
5 different games are played: bridge, go, backgammon, scrabble, poker
City: marseilles, paris, liverpool, london, hamburg
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person traveling to paris##2
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person playing backgammon##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing poker##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Game       | poker | bridge | backgammon  | scrabble | go    |
| City       | liverpool        | london   | paris  | hamburg   | marseilles |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

