.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, daisy, orchid, dahlia
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, tiparillo, old-henry, cain, montecristo
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is between the person watching crime movies and the person who growsdaisy##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person who growsdahlia and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 7. the cain-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Flower           | poppy | daisy | orchid | dahlia    | rose  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | tiparillo        | alhambra   | cain    | montecristo     |

