.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: marseillesd-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
There are 5 different nationalities: american, brazilian, dutch, egyptian, indonesian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, oliveros, bolivar, aristoff
City: prague, marseilles, miami, paris, venice
 1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the brazilian##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
 5. the blend-smoker is between the american and the montecristo-smoker##2
 6. the american is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is marseillesd-games##2
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is marseillesd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is marseillesd-games is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | marseillesd-games |
| Nationality   | american   | egyptian    | brazilian | indonesian | dutch      |
| Cigar           | oliveros | blend    | montecristo       | bolivar     | aristoff      |
| City     | miami | venice        | prague  | marseilles        | paris    |

