.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, cricket-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, baseball, parkour, ice-hockey, cricket
There 5 different types of food: pepper, artichoke, apricot, blueberry, cranberry
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person eating blueberry and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person eating cranberry and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 6. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cricket-climbing is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person who's hobby is cricket-climbing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | cricket-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Sport   | parkour | climbing    | cricket    | ice-hockey       | baseball         |
| Food   | blueberry  | artichoke | cranberry    | apricot     | pepper      |

 